name: jcn
params: wff w0, wff w1, wff w2

body.origin:
|- wi(w0, wn(wi(w1, w2)))
-| wi(w0, wn(wi(w1, wn(wn(w2)))))
-| wb(wi(w1, w2), wi(w1, wn(wn(w2))))

cumulated.origin:
|- wi(w0, wn(wi(w1, w2)))
-| wi(w0, wn(wi(w1, wn(wn(w2)))))
-| wb(wi(w1, w2), wi(w1, wn(wn(w2))))

body.origin:
|- wi(w0, wn(wi(w1, wn(wn(w2)))))
-| wi(w0, w1)
-| wi(w0, wn(w2))

cumulated.origin:
|- wi(w0, wn(wi(w1, w2)))
-| wb(wi(w1, w2), wi(w1, wn(wn(w2))))
-| wi(w0, w1)
-| wi(w0, wn(w2))

body.origin:
|- wb(wi(w1, w2), wi(w1, wn(wn(w2))))
-| wb(w2, wn(wn(w2)))

cumulated.origin:
|- wi(w0, wn(wi(w1, w2)))
-| wi(w0, w1)
-| wi(w0, wn(w2))
-| wb(w2, wn(wn(w2)))

comment: Inference joining the consequents of two premises. (Contributed by Glauco Siliprandi, 11-Dec-2019.)
